From e3d91a681cb5bcf283bc9c8647ba56aede69a38a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Benjamin Berg <benjamin.berg@intel.com>
Date: Thu, 2 Jan 2025 16:20:04 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] wifi: mac80211: pass correct link ID on assoc
Git-commit: e3d91a681cb5bcf283bc9c8647ba56aede69a38a
Patch-mainline: v6.14-rc1
References: jsc#PED-14425

The link ID passed to drv_mgd_complete_tx when handling the association
response was not set.

Signed-off-by: Benjamin Berg <benjamin.berg@intel.com>
Reviewed-by: Johannes Berg <johannes.berg@intel.com>
Signed-off-by: Miri Korenblit <miriam.rachel.korenblit@intel.com>
Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20250102161730.2b06504ecaef.Ifb94e9375b910de6cdd2e5865d8cb3ab9790b314@changeid
Signed-off-by: Johannes Berg <johannes.berg@intel.com>
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

---
 net/mac80211/mlme.c | 2 ++
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)

diff --git a/net/mac80211/mlme.c b/net/mac80211/mlme.c
index 2286eea18aed..9bc0db308a96 100644
--- a/net/mac80211/mlme.c
+++ b/net/mac80211/mlme.c
@@ -5976,6 +5976,8 @@ static void ieee80211_rx_mgmt_assoc_resp(struct ieee80211_sub_if_data *sdata,
 	if (!assoc_data)
 		return;
 
+	info.link_id = assoc_data->assoc_link_id;
+
 	parse_params.mode =
 		assoc_data->link[assoc_data->assoc_link_id].conn.mode;
 
-- 
